          "url": "https://wikem.org/wiki/SVT"
        }
      ]
    },
    "Pediatric_Dosing": {
      "text": "Afib\n/\nflutter\n,\nSVT\nIV 0.1-0.2 (<1yo) or 0.1-0.3 (>1yo) mg/kg. Repeat after 30 minutes if inadequate response\nPO: 4-10 mg/kg/day in 3 divided doses",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
