    "Mechanism_of_Action": {
      "text": "Inhibits L-type (slow) calcium channels, blocking influx of calcium into myocardial cells\nReduces systemic vascular resistance, vasodiolates peripheral arteries",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
      "links": []
